<section id="assumptions" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="assumptions">Assumptions</h3>
<p>This model assumes a “perfectly mixed” pool where every quarter in the metro area has an equal chance of landing in your pocket. In reality, quarters might cluster in local businesses or laundromats, potentially increasing the local probability even further!</p>


